{"id": "1402298572552015883", "channel_id": "1402298572552015883", "type": 0, "author_id": "1400438508866371606", "author_name": "shjnov", "author_bot": false, "content": "最近回坑的玩家，box和命轮如下，包里有3个原型3个母版1个原点，想求补启建议🙏\n主要玩杜勒赛因，塔薇，凯刻斯，卡在第九章9-5了该怎么打啊。\n我用塔薇和杜勒都没打过，六翼打不出伤害，是我操作的问题嘛？打女王之剑感觉还刮了些伤害…开一个大才减boss十几力量，站不住，第一条命没打死就爆灵智了。不能删牌，杜勒队因为我box不齐带的雷娅那张3再加迟缓4费一直占在手里…\n特别无力后面的关还能打过嘛😳哪个队伍好打呢，有没有视频可以让我学习一下操作🥹🥹", "timestamp": "2025-08-05T14:33:53.144000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1402298573084688504", "filename": "IMG_7194.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 879909, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1402298572552015883/1402298573084688504/IMG_7194.png?ex=69cd2cd1&is=69cbdb51&hm=44f2aca75df4f44a53118211829335fc89f92b9859bb726560b8f1ea33e59270&"}, {"id": "1402298573546196992", "filename": "IMG_7195.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 870689, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1402298572552015883/1402298573546196992/IMG_7195.png?ex=69cd2cd1&is=69cbdb51&hm=805cb7e9b42a476eff94cdc99f94793ff0fcb2fae466e0e945f3dd63d3796fa6&"}, {"id": "1402298573969690794", "filename": "IMG_7196.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 885691, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1402298572552015883/1402298573969690794/IMG_7196.png?ex=69cd2cd1&is=69cbdb51&hm=b94a2eac81e9d08547d715949e20e0778f49aa39309714a192454b6e7585b19d&"}, {"id": "1402298574452031658", "filename": "IMG_7197.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 705770, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1402298572552015883/1402298574452031658/IMG_7197.png?ex=69cd2cd1&is=69cbdb51&hm=1472b0c2e2abc6ed27f9aae5e73beb0fbd82333aedd8ec743cd52c0d4fd7d7de&"}, {"id": "1402298575089827890", "filename": "IMG_7198.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1806747, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1402298572552015883/1402298575089827890/IMG_7198.png?ex=69cd2cd1&is=69cbdb51&hm=538b6153b8569726238c84fd24